overview.en: Cred is a decentralized global financial platform that facilitates open access to inclusive finance anywhere and anytime, harness the power of blockchain to allow everyone to benefit from low-cost financial products and crypto economy.
overview.zh: Cred是一个基于区块链和加密数字货币的金融生态系统，帮助全球的加密数字货币用户，随时随地高效地享受各类金融服务，比如理财CredEarn和借贷CredBorrow。
